  "reference_number": "GAC0072",
  "remarks": "\nEVRAZIA is an involved person under the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis of the following grounds: (1) EVRAZIA is acting on behalf of or at the direction of Ilan Shor; (2) EVRAZIA is associated with Ilan Shor. Ilan Shor is an involved person under the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis that he has been involved in serious corruption, namely being responsible for or engaging in serious corruption with respect to bribery of foreign public officials.\n",
